attributes.title: The Body Bag
attributes.description: Aaron and Chris challenge each other to drag a body bag across the city from their apartment to the river in less than 30 minutes... With a little help from innocent bystanders.

attributes.title: The Sex Survey Experiment
attributes.description: Chris and Aaron conduct a sex survey and attempt to sign people up for a sexual deviancy class...however, they wrote each other's survey, and have no idea what the questions are beforehand.

attributes.title: The Speed Dating Challenge
attributes.description: Chris and Aaron go speed dating and compete to see who can match up with the most people... The twist is that they each wrote note-cards for each other and must do whatever the cards say before each date.

attributes.title: The Garage Sale
attributes.description: Chris and Aaron compete to see who can make the most money at a garage sale. However, Aaron is only allowed to sell serial killer merchandise while Chris must somehow sell celebrity stalker memorabilia.

attributes.title: The Limo Tour
attributes.description: Aaron and Chris give tours of Austin in a run-down limo. However, they don't know the tour stops, because when one is the tour guide, the other is the chauffeur driving the limo.

attributes.title: The Escaped Prisoner
attributes.description: Chris and Aaron escape jail, and must travel from the Austin Police Department to the train station in under two hours...while wearing handcuffs and asking for money.
